sub_title: Principal Depth Imaging Geophysicist at Shell
summary:
Specialties: depth imaging, vel/depth model-building for Pre-SDM, TZ-conversion, seismic processing, teaching PSDM + vel/depth model-building courses, coaching junior/senior staff.

Shell 'Subject Matter Expert' (SME) on depth imaging and velocity modelling. 
SME on time-depth conversion (specialisation on depth uncertainties)
